summary: A Mysterio piece I keep forgetting to upload haha. I’m really excited for this movie and for him! I haven’t been this excited...
body: A Mysterio piece I keep forgetting to upload haha. I’m really excited for this movie and for him! I haven’t been this excited about a villain in a while. Also I don’t know how Marvel did it, but somehow they took one of their most ridiculous villains in comic book history and made me think “he’s hot” on first appearance. That’s gotta win some awards.
